<br>
The message boards say it is very similar to EQ but with some of the problems worked out a little better...such as questing and class balancing. Any game that has fixed Verant's &quot;block feet&quot; graphics and the cross-legged sitting graphic and can implement capes must be on the right track.  <a href=http://camelot.stratics.com/content/sod/02122001.jpg target="web">ScreenShot</a><br>
<br>
Check out this web page for more screenshots and some basic info.<br>
<a href=http://camelot.stratics.com target="web">Camelot Stratics</a><br>
<br>
Harrison Abbeyroad<br>
