<br>
<br>
It seams to rerstricting. It also add the dissadvantage that if I pick a race/class combo that suits my desires...I may or may not be able to play with friends. Especially if their race/class is an oposing faction.<br>
<br>
<br>
I would ecpect more races and classes in a system that forces PvP upon oposing factions.<br>
<br>
<br>
I may or may not play DAoC. I play MMORPG for many reasons. Prolly the biggest is tha feact that my RL friends and I tend to play together. If few of my friends will be playing then I prolly wont enjoy. <br>
